  <diagram id="p1" name="1. Requirements Diagram (BY-55)">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1422" dy="762" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1660" pageHeight="860" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0"/>
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0"/>
        <mxCell id="rt" value="YogaBook — SysML Requirements Diagram (BY-55)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;fontStyle=1;fontSize=16;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="360" y="20" width="960" height="40" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="rsys" value="&lt;&lt;system&gt;&gt;
YogaBook Booking System" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="590" y="80" width="380" height="60" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r01" value="REQ-01  &lt;&lt;requirement&gt;&gt;
User Authentication

The system shall support secure
user authentication." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="200" width="250" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r02" value="REQ-02  &lt;&lt;requirement&gt;&gt;
Venue Management

The system shall allow admins
to manage yoga venues." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="330" y="200" width="250" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r03" value="REQ-03  &lt;&lt;requirement&gt;&gt;
Session Management

The system shall allow admins
to manage yoga sessions." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="620" y="200" width="250" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r04" value="REQ-04  &lt;&lt;requirement&gt;&gt;
Booking System

The system shall allow members
to book yoga sessions." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="910" y="200" width="250" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r05" value="REQ-05  &lt;&lt;requirement&gt;&gt;
Membership Management

The system shall manage
membership plans." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1200" y="200" width="250" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec_r01" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;startArrow=diamond;startFill=1;endArrow=none;startSize=8;" edge="1" source="rsys" target="r01" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec_r02" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;startArrow=diamond;startFill=1;endArrow=none;startSize=8;" edge="1" source="rsys" target="r02" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec_r03" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;startArrow=diamond;startFill=1;endArrow=none;startSize=8;" edge="1" source="rsys" target="r03" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec_r04" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;startArrow=diamond;startFill=1;endArrow=none;startSize=8;" edge="1" source="rsys" target="r04" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ec_r05" value="" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;startArrow=diamond;startFill=1;endArrow=none;startSize=8;" edge="1" source="rsys" target="r05" parent="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r011" value="REQ-01.1  id=01.1

Register
Users shall register
with email and password." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r012" value="REQ-01.2  id=01.2

Login + JWT
Users shall log in
and receive a JWT token." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="220" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r013" value="REQ-01.3  id=01.3

Role-Based Access Control
System enforces RBAC:
Guest, Member, Admin roles." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="420" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r021" value="REQ-02.1  id=02.1

Admin CRUD
Admins shall create, edit
and deactivate venues." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="620" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r022" value="REQ-02.2  id=02.2

Public Browse
All users shall be able
to browse active venues." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="820" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r031" value="REQ-03.1  id=03.1

Create Sessions
Admins shall create sessions
with venue, time, capacity." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1020" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r032" value="REQ-03.2  id=03.2

Recurring Sessions
Admins shall configure
weekly recurring sessions." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1220" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r033" value="REQ-03.3  id=03.3

View Timetable
Users shall view sessions
filtered by venue and date." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1420" y="380" width="190" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r041" value="REQ-04.1  id=04.1

Book Session
Members with active membership
shall book sessions." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r042" value="REQ-04.2  id=04.2

Cancel Booking
Members shall cancel
upcoming bookings." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="230" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r043" value="REQ-04.3  id=04.3

Booking History
Members shall view
their booking history." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="440" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r051" value="REQ-05.1  id=05.1

Membership Plans
Admin shall define
membership plan options." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="650" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r052" value="REQ-05.2  id=05.2

Purchase and Renew
Members shall purchase
and renew memberships." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="860" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r053" value="REQ-05.3  id=05.3

Membership Required
Active membership shall
be required to book." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#e8f4fe;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1070" y="560" width="200" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
